## User Story

As a **user**, I want to **be able to filter items by category**, so that I can easily find the items I am interested in.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 1**: A dropdown should be added to the UI for selecting categories.
- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 2**: The list of items should update based on the selected category.

## Tasks

- [ ] **Task 1**: Implement the filter UI in the front-end.
- [ ] **Task 2**: Update the back-end API to support category filtering.
- [ ] **Task 3**: Test the feature with different categories.

## Additional Information

- **Priority**: High
- **Related Issues**: #101
- **Dependencies**: None

## Notes

Ensure the feature is responsive and works well on mobile devices.
